=== Data Collection and Use

PDF READER does not collect, transfer, sell personal information such as your name, email address, phone number, credit card, information about usage app or any other data. 

=== Permissions with explanation

READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE and WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE (Android pre 11) or MANAGE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE (Android 11+) - to read and write files on external storage (SD card, USB flash);
INTERNET - to display third-party advertising and marketing

=== Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes.

